text: hey as a food content creator i've been
so ashamed of my messy fridge i always
wish i had the pristine clean fridges
from the tiktok videos but mine has been
looking like this for so long so this
week i decided to give my messy fridge a
makeover to be honest with you i've been
generating a lot of food waste largely
because i was so unorganized and
couldn't keep track of what groceries i
had too much of and oftentimes i'd have
to throw out what went bad and i'm not
proud of it and i wanted to fix this
once and for all so i emptied out my
fridge took out all the shelves sanitize
the inside sanitize the shelves and
bought some containers to help me
compartmentalize and easily take out
items in the back of my fridge and in
the end i finally did it
just for comparison this is a before and
after and then i also installed some led
lights whenever i needed to film more
content and i was happier than when i
lit my christmas tree last winter follow
to see the final first stock video i
made with my new fridge
